## 9. Awareness Repair

### 9.1 Resolution Increase
Sharpen visibility.

### 9.2 Gradient Illumination
Reveal hidden structures.

### 9.3 Boundary Stabilization
Prevent awareness leakage.

### 9.4 Recursive Reorientation
Redirect awareness loops.

### 9.5 Continuity Enforcement
Maintain stable visibility across time.

Repair restores awareness coherence.

---

## 10. Summary
Awareness defines:
- visibility  
- resolution  
- accessibility  
- stability  
- recursive illumination  

Awareness is the **visibility architecture** of cognition — the structure that determines what the system can perceive, understand, and transform.
